{"tid":1488911,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家唔好唔記得我哋有對方春袋可以錫","createTime":"2019-08-19T17:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T13:22:00.000Z","uid":11587,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"38393ae7588ca06b4252223e83cf6a304d7b3cb0","tid":1488911,"uid":11587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:34:33.000Z","msg":"入嚟嘅人俾小小時間睇下？<br />\n<br />\n睇到有人取消咗機場活動<br />\n<br />\n其實唔明點解唔繼續去機場，又冇咩人講<br />\n機場對我哋咁有利，又擺明係春袋嚟喎<br />\n<br />\n1.唔驚有人會受傷<br />\n2.唔會有多人被捕<br />\n3.可以將我方嘅損失減到最低<br />\n4.要攬炒嘅又可以攬炒到盡<br />\n5.想和理非嘅又極有效（點都勁過去地鐵不合作）<br />\n6.仲有冷氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咁好嘅籌碼點解唔繼續用？<br />\n<br />\n今個星期嘅遊行集會唔改去機場我都明白<br />\n我都唔想分散人手，但我哋應該要選擇效用最大，成本最低嘅做法架嘛，所以大家之後主力去機場得唔得呢？<br />\n<br />\nBtw，我見好多人同其他人持不同意見就標籤對方做鬼，咪再沉迷捉鬼啦大家<br />\n捉鬼等如俾藉口自己同人割𥱊啊！意見唔同唔緊要！要傾架嘛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警還眼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5647685b20b6294c38bdc274c4d78c9335e78fc1","tid":1488911,"uid":11587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:36:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0730bdd1e9fb38bea051b338eb4cb481dbc2070c","tid":1488911,"uid":11587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:36:16.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"4688558c600ef2a32b5bfd07ed1c3776f16abdec","tid":1488911,"uid":276888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:36:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006ed98835cdaeadc49e280dcf8ef2b2658dfd1f","tid":1488911,"uid":293700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:36:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"285f0212e680c9aec29d7e0cdf990627f70e5747","tid":1488911,"uid":121855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:37:00.000Z","msg":"岩呀！！機場根本就係一個最低成本最高效能嘅抗爭手段"},{"pid":"d7370e37ecadcdc29ae6855bf7410aaf4f874606","tid":1488911,"uid":276888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:37:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b19b6c33a8c2db0de5a670bf7444b794c822054","tid":1488911,"uid":11587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:37:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af77a8fc295ab91978f78741a991a188c19ff528","tid":1488911,"uid":102108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:38:17.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7299d9b2b44d9da66abd2391e3fb520d5835d963","tid":1488911,"uid":11587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbf82714736cc1265a4dd163b02d16cf9c506e9","tid":1488911,"uid":295889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:39:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">認真理性討論post冇人睇！？  大家幫手入嚟投票 </span></span><br />\nSet死線通牒林奠再升級係大多手足嘅共識 大家入嚟公投同討下啦 要過5,000正評 民間記者會應該要反映到抗爭者主流意見同策略<br />\n冇網絡大軍同P牌不能投 要靠大家！！<br />\n<br />\n【改良版】連登公投：民間記者會宣佈休戰並設限通牒林奠908答應訴求否則